                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Practice Responsible Driving:</span> Avoid distractions, always follow speed limits, and prioritize safety.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Check Vehicle Fitness:</span> Especially for older vehicles, timely fitness checks are now essential to avoid fines.</li>
